data.description: Wonderful 3 bed/2 bath home with TWO living areas! The open layout is perfect for any size family plus an extra large living room with wood burning fireplace and easy to maintain laminate flooring.  New windows, new light fixtures, new water heater, fresh paint and other updates! Not included in the spacious 1821 SF is an additional 300+ SF of an enclosed patio area, perfect for any hobby or storage! Outside features a new storage shed, generous lot and 2-vehicle carport.  This home checks all the boxes!
